text: Frederic Orendi (12 March 1930 - 1998) was a Romanian gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:1998 deaths Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Mediaș
